--------------------------------------------------------
For installation

$ git clone https://github.com/karinmaths/sample_app

After clone
$ bundle install

Run these command before test
$ bundle exec rake db:reset
$ bundle exec rake db:populate
$ bundle exec rake db:test:prepare

Test
$ bundle exec guard
